{"type": "article", "id": 21692, "title": "Brooklyn Desk by Oeuf", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-02T07:34:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122306IoUEivbjLPxa739d.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">法国设计工作室 OEUF 专为儿童设计家具，这是他们新推出的给儿童的桌子。采用波罗的海的桦木胶合板，白色搭配木头的自然色，简单而干净。桌子的边缘有3个可移动的木盒子，放零碎的文具用品，很方便。桌子的高度是可调的，能调整到适合成人使用。售价 575 美元，<a href=\"http://www.oeufnyc.com/index.php/furniture/brooklyn-desk.html\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122304zsKYoLBikW5HOvde.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122304q3MZlWLQ6CNOt02R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.21166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122305r7VHoUT5L2g96RBv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122305X7u1NqBtGJjrapdM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}